'''筋膜'''是贯穿身体的一层[[纤维结缔组织|纤维结缔组织]]（疏松或緻密结缔组织），它衬垫在皮肤底下，及包绕着肌肉、肌群、血管、神经、内脏。<ref name="Marieb-133">{{cite book
 |title=Human anatomy & physiology
 |author=Marieb, Elaine Nicpon; Hoehn, Katja
 |publisher=Pearson Education
 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=x1uEB68iitwC&pg=PA133
 |page=133
 |date=2007
 |isbn=9780321372949
 |access-date=2010-09-24
 |archive-date=2021-03-10
 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310162555/https://books.google.com/books?id=x1uEB68iitwC&pg=PA133
 |dead-url=no
 }}</ref>筋膜分为三种，分别叫浅筋膜、深筋膜、内脏筋膜（漿膜下筋膜），它们延绵不断贯穿身体上下。<ref name="sport-fitness-advisor">{{cite web
 |title=Self Myofascial Release
 |url=http://www.sport-fitness-advisor.com/self-myofascial-release.html
 |accessdate=2010-08-17
 |archive-date=2021-02-26
 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226215223/https://www.sport-fitness-advisor.com/self-myofascial-release.html
 |dead-url=no
 }}</ref>

筋膜主体是是纤维结缔组织，其内可含脂肪组织、血管与神经。疏松结缔组织主要在浅筋膜及内脏筋膜处；緻密结缔组织主要在深筋膜处，其内含紧密规则排列的[[胶原纤维|胶原纤维]]，胶原纤维的方向是顺着拉力的方向，所以，深筋膜具有很强的单向抗拉性能。<ref name="Marieb-133" />

